                                        </style>
                                      </textItem>
                                      <textItem>
                                        <dataSource>
                                          <staticValue>One of the parameters in this report (_as_of_date) allows your users to choose the As Of Date for their reports. By default, the As Of Date is "today's" date.</staticValue>
                                        </dataSource>
                                      </textItem>
                                      <textItem>
                                        <dataSource>
                                          <staticValue>For more information, see </staticValue>
